          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">GKM Industries Inc</span> <span class="text-war-text-dim">(George Moncayo)</span> — Asbestos abatement (ACM Roof Membrane and Flashing)</div>
          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">ERPM Co.</span> <span class="text-war-text-dim">(Mira Labiscase, Charles Dachs)</span> — Property management, proposals, payment processing</div>
          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">Rhini Solutions LLC</span> — Air monitoring</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card space-y-3 mb-4">
        <div class="font-mono text-xxs text-war-amber uppercase tracking-widest">Deliverables by HD Contractors Corp (Base Scope)</div>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-war-text-dim">
          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">Work Area 1: Temporary Roof Membrane</span> — Clean wood decking substrate. Install Siplast Primer with TA-119. Install Siplast SA vapor retarder. Install peel and stick roofing membrane over entire existing roof.</div>
          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">Work Area 2: Removal of Steel Beams</span> — Install protection on roof. Cut steel beams into small pieces and remove.</div>
          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">Work Area 3: Stucco (600 sf)</span> — Sound all cracks and demo loose stucco from both sides. Install mesh wire via gun anchors. Apply single coat of stucco.</div>
          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">Work Area 4: Sidewalk Caulking Repair</span> — Remove existing damaged caulking. Install new caulking around sidewalk joints.</div>
          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">Work Area 5: Scrape, Prime and Paint Steel Railing</span> — Protect area with tarp. Electric scrape. Apply Rustoleum Primer. Apply 2 coats paint.</div>
          <div><span class="text-war-text font-medium">Work Area 6: Chimney Demo</span> — Demo existing leaning chimney up to roof level. Install proper closing protocol.</div>
